## Memory kerja

Memory kerja ada di folder `memory/`. Index ada di `memory/MEMORY.md`.

**Kapan baca memory:**
- {{USER_NAME}} tanya sesuatu tentang project/tugas → baca `memory/MEMORY.md` dulu
- {{USER_NAME}} bilang "ingat ini" / "catat" → simpan ke file memory baru

**Cara simpan memory baru:**
Tulis file ke `memory/{category}/{slug}.md` dengan frontmatter:
```
---
name: nama singkat
description: deskripsi 1 baris
type: project | task | note | user
---
```
Lalu tambah pointer di `memory/MEMORY.md`.

